Patch Set 9: Code-Review+1

I believe a backport to Kilo would be appropriate for this bug. It just adds back the unique constraints to the metadef tables that were there in the beginning. It does not touch any other tables and should not have any adverse side-effects on the image side. Not having the unique constraints is much worse.
